# RBAC

Role-Based Access Control generated by MyCLI.

## Tables

- roles
- permissions
- role_permissions
- user_roles

## CLI

```bash
my role create admin
my permission create user.read
my permission assign admin user.read
my role assign <userId> admin
```

## Middleware

Use `createRbacMiddleware(rbac)` for `role`, `permission`, and `can` guards.
